      "name": "2. Property Registration (with RabbitMQ)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register Property - Test 1",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test(\"Status code is 201\", function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test(\"Response has property data\", function () {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('matriculaId');",
                  "    pm.expect(jsonData.matriculaId).to.eql(111222);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "// Save property ID for later use",
                  "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.environment.set('property_id', jsonData.id);",
                  "pm.environment.set('matricula_id', jsonData.matriculaId);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"matriculaId\": 111222,\n  \"folha\": 100,\n  \"comarca\": \"S√£o Paulo - SP\",\n  \"endereco\": \"Rua RabbitMQ Test, 100\",\n  \"metragem\": 250,\n  \"proprietario\": \"0x565524f400856766f11562832eB809d889491a01\",\n  \"matriculaOrigem\": 0,\n  \"tipo\": \"URBANO\",\n  \"isRegular\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{orchestrator_url}}/api/properties/register",
              "host": ["{{orchestrator_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "properties", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Registra propriedade no banco e envia job REGISTER_PROPERTY para RabbitMQ.\n\n**Fluxo Esperado:**\n1. ‚úÖ Salva no PostgreSQL (core_orchestrator_db)\n2. üì§ Publica job na fila blockchain-jobs\n3. ‚è≥ Queue Worker processa\n4. ‚úÖ Offchain API registra na blockchain"
